_size, build_time\n259:   - Verify metadata updated with image info\n260: \n261: - [ ] **TEST-003**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_missing_dockerfile` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n262:   - Call build with workspace without Dockerfile\n263:   - Verify ValueError raised with \"Dockerfile not found\" message\n264: \n265: - [ ] **TEST-004**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_docker_unavailable` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n266:   - Mock docker_service.check_docker_available to return False\n267:   - Verify RuntimeError raised with \"Docker is not available\" message\n268: \n269: - [ ] **TEST-005**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_version_increment` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n270:   - Create workspace with version 1.2.3\n271:   - Call build\n272:   - Verify version incremented to 1.2.4 in metadata\n273: \n274: - [ ] **TEST-006**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_version_rollback_on_failure` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n275:   - Mock docker_service.build_image to raise exception\n276:   - Verify build fails\n277:   - Verify version reverted to original\n278: \n279: - [ ] **TEST-007**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_cloud_mode` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n280:   - Call build with cloud_provider=\"huawei\"\n281:   - Verify cloud build path taken\n282:   - Verify result has cloud-specific image_name\n283: \n284: - [ ] **TEST-008**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_unsupported_cloud_provider` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n285:   - Call build with cloud_provider=\"unknown\"\n286:   - Verify ValueError raised\n287: \n288: - [ ] **TEST-009**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_proxy_configuration` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n289:   - Call build with proxy=\"http://proxy:port\"\n290:   - Verify build_args include HTTP_PROXY and HTTPS_PROXY\n291: \n292: - [ ] **TEST-010**: Implement `TestBuildRuntime.test_build_prerelease_version_increment` in `test_build_runtime.py`\n293:   - Create workspace with version 1.0.0-alpha.1\n294:   - Call build